Package gov.ca.water.calgui.bo

In this package we have the Business objects like AuditBO, DataTableModel etc..

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AuditBO
    This is holding the information for Audit.
    DataTableModel
    This class is used to hold the tables for the application.
    DSSGrabber1BO
    Class to grab (load) DSS time series for a set of scenarios passed in a JList.
    DSSGrabber2BO
    Class to grab (generate) DSS time series BASED ON DTS list for a set of scenarios passed in a JList.
    FileDialogBO
    Supports selection of different types of CalLite files from customized JFileChoosers.
    GUILinks2BO
    This is used to hold the information of GUI_Link2.table in memory.
    GUILinks3BO
    This is used to hold the information of GUI_Links3.csv in memory.
    GUILinks4BO
    This is used to hold the information of GUI_Link4.table in memory.
    JLinkedSlider
    This class extends the Swing JSlider class by linking a slider to a "left" and a "right" JTextBox.
    NumericTextField
    This class is used to only enter the numeric values in the text field.
    RBListItemBO
    RBListItem is a helper for the FileDialog class.
    ResultUtilsBO
    Supporting utilities for display of results
    ScenarioDisplayBO
    This will hold the intermediate information used for building the Scenario Display.
    SimpleFileFilter
    Custom file filter class for use in CalLite GUI
    TriggerBO
    This is used to hold the information of Trigger*.table in memory.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CalLiteGUIException
    I am the root exception for CalLiteGUI.
